OL,3,C'Everything's on the line' say
OL,4,Csteelworkers as they take fight to
OL,5,CWestminster
OL,7,FSteelworkers say "everything's on the
OL,8,Fline" as they head to Westminster to
OL,9,Fdemonstrate over Tata's decision to
OL,10,Fcut jobs in south Wales.
OL,12,FThe steel giant's global CEO T.V.
OL,13,FNarendran and UK CEO Rajesh Nair will
OL,14,Fappear before members of the Welsh
OL,15,FAffairs Select Committee today.
OL,17,FThe company announced almost two weeks
OL,18,Fago plans to close both its blast
OL,19,Ffurnaces at its Port Talbot site with
OL,20,Fthe loss of around 2,500 jobs.
