OL,3,C'Everything's on the line' say
OL,4,Csteelworkers as they take fight to
OL,5,CWestminster
OL,7,FA further 300 posts will be cut
OL,8,Felsewhere as the industry moves
OL,9,Ftowards a greener way of making steel.
OL,11,FStarting "economic activity" in the
OL,12,Farea as soon as possible is a
OL,13,Fpriority, according to the CEO, with
OL,14,Fthe company already in discussions
OL,15,Fwith "potential equipment suppliers."
OL,17,FHe added: "If you spend a billion
OL,18,Fpounds on building something here, a
OL,19,Flot of that money will float to the
OL,20,Flocal economy."
