OL,7,FUnions had offered an alternative
OL,8,Fplan, which meant keeping one blast
OL,9,Ffurnace open until 2032, but Tata did
OL,10,Fnot feel this was a viable
OL,11,Falternative, saying "Apart from being
OL,12,Fmore expensive, it had operational
OL,13,Fchallenges."
OL,15,FSteel union representatives from the
OL,16,FGMB, Community and Unite will be among
OL,17,Fthe witnesses today.
