OL,7,F"The UK has gone from a huge steel
OL,8,Fexporter 15 years ago, to now
OL,9,Fimporting #2billion worth every year.
OL,10,FSoon we won't even be able to make
OL,11,Fprimary steel in this country.
OL,13,F"It's a national disgrace."
OL,15,FLast night steelworkers and union
OL,16,Fmembers gathered in Port Talbot to
OL,17,Fdiscuss the industry's future.
